com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree.utils

Class BehaviorTreeLibraryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree.utils.BehaviorTreeLibraryManager

  • public class BehaviorTreeLibraryManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The BehaviorTreeLibraryManager is a singleton in charge of the creation of behavior trees using the underlying library. If no library is explicitly set (see the method setLibrary(BehaviorTreeLibrary)), a default library using the InternalFileHandleResolver is used.
